data.text:
Two Days Three Stages and Over Thirty Bands makes Stanstock the Ultimate Family Reunion and #1 Maryland Music Fest! Music starts at 12 Noon Both Days and goes All Day Long. Stages Inside and Out. Bands Include: ALO: Atomoic Light Orchestra,Awaken, John Christ, Cinema, Eclipse: A Journey Tribute, and More. All proceeds go to the Nicole Van Horn Foundation benefiting children with cancer and The Catch A Lift Fund. Find out more HERE.

Musicians, this is the opportunity you’ve been waiting for! Stages Music Arts, Baltimore’s premiere recording studio, is giving away free studio time and a chance to film a music video in our state-of-the-art facility. Whether you’re a solo artist or part of a band, now is your chance to shine. To enter, submit your demo at stagesmusicarts.com. Don’t miss out on this amazing chance to record your music and create a video professionally—completely FREE! Enter HERE.

Get Ready For Double The Food… Double The Drinks…And Double The Fun…100.7 The Bay And WJZ TV Proudly Present The 2nd Annual Maryland Crabcake Festival… Coming To The Carroll County Farm Museum In Westminster on Saturday October 26th! Indulge Yourself In Maryland’s Best Crabcakes And Food Trucks. Enjoy An Adult Beverage From The Best Craft Breweries And Wineries Around. And Rock Out To Live Music FromThe Amish Outlaws, Doc Marten And The Flannels and National Recording Artist Jimmy Charles.

Get Ready For Double The Food… Double The Drinks…And Double The Fun…Bigger… Better… And Back! For It’s Second Year…100.7 The Bay And WJZ TV Proudly Present The 2nd Annual Maryland Crabcake Festival, Coming To The Carroll County Farm Museum In Westminster, On Saturday October 26th…Listen for your shot at a pair of General Admission tickets this Thursday 7/11 from 6am-6pm . Listen on 100.7, 107.5 in Harford County or The Bay mobile app for your chance to win.

Join Matt & 100.7 The Bay at Jimmy’s Famous TailGOAT with ROCK & WRESTLING Saturday June 15th. This Father’s Day Weekend Spectacle will highlight many facets of what makeAmerica so special: Baseball, Pro Wrestling, Delicious Food, Refreshing Cocktails, Family Bonding, and amazing music from The 80s & 90s!For tickets & info, click HERE.
